latestPosts.caption:
Craving a break that’s not just about “doing more,” but about feeling more YOU?

Return Home is a 3nights/4days yoga retreat in Kerala designed to help you slow down, soften, and reconnect - with yourself, with nature, and with others.

🧘‍♀️ Expect:
✔️ Guided meditative dining experiences
✔️ Ice bath by the river (hello nervous system reset)
✔️ Evening canoe rides on the Periyar at sunset
✔️ Soulful Kerala meals (veg & non-veg!)
✔️ Breathwork, stillness & soft community

This isn’t a detox. It’s a return - to yourself. To your breath. To your pace.

📍Vedic Village, Kerala
🗓️ June 20–23, 2025
🔗 Link in bio for full details + early bird info

#yogaretreatindia #keralaretreat #spiritualretreat #slowtravelindia #yogaretreat2025 #womensretreat #yogaretreatkerala #healingretreat #mindfulmovement #stillnesspractice #returnhome #keralayoga #yogainkerala

If you’ve been meaning to take a break, pause, or just breathe a little deeper — my sister @shivaanishashi is hosting a 4-day yoga retreat this June that’s all heart.

It’s called Return Home, and it’s happening at Vedic Village, Kerala — a place we’ve poured so much love into as a family.

This isn’t your typical retreat. Think: slow mornings, yoga that feels good, honest conversations, soulful food, and a chance to come back to you.

🗓 June 20–23
📍Vedic Village, Kerala
📞+918714642807

Highly recommend it if you’re looking to reset. 

DM her if you’re curious.

latestPosts.caption:
The boat waits. So do I.
Are you ready to drift inward?

Where the backwaters don’t just carry you through history of Kerala — they carry you back to yourself.

🗓️June 20-23 | Return Home Retreat
📍Vedic Village | Kerala

This retreat isn’t just a getaway.
It’s a gentle remembering.
A return home… to yourself! 

[backwaters, kerala, yogaretreat, yoga, yogateacher, breakfromlife]

Not your regular yoga teacher! 😎

Bringing you yoga in a way that actually makes sense—digestible, relatable, and rooted in real life.
Because yoga isn’t just about calm faces and quiet meditation—it’s about learning how to come back to yourself… again and again.

Return Home is a soulful 3-night retreat in Kerala designed for deep rest, real connection, and gentle movement that meets you where you are.

🧘‍♀️ Expect:
✔️ Guided meditative dining experiences
✔️ Ice bath by the river (hello nervous system)
✔️ Canoe rides on the Periyar at sunset
✔️ Soulful Kerala meals (veg & non-veg)
✔️ Breathwork, stillness & soft community

This isn’t a detox. It’s a remembering.

📍 Vedic Village, Kerala
🗓️ June 20–23, 2025
🔗 Link in bio for details — DM Return Home for special offer info.

#yogaretreatindia #keralayoga #relatableyoga #realpractice #notjustasanas #yogawithshivaani #healingretreat #mindfulmovement #returnhome

The biggest struggle I have faced in India, when I say I do yoga…

Yoga is still seen as something boring. Just sitting still. Just meditating.

But yoga is so much more. It’s breath. It’s movement. It’s inquiry. It’s expression.
It’s not about escaping life - it’s about learning how to actually be in it.

DM “ICE BOAT” to get all the info sent straight to your inbox.

Turned a boat into an ice bath. Because a tub felt too basic. 🤷‍♀️

June 20-23
Vedic Village, Kerala
Join me? 🥶

Feeling overwhelmed, wired, or worn out? This 2 hours workshop is a pause button for your nervous system. 

Join Shivaani Shashi, (International yoga teacher with experience of teaching over 3000+ hours across Bali, Thailand & India) for an immersive stress relief session that blends gentle movement, breathwork, and practical tools you can carry into everyday life.

Together, we’ll move, breathe, reflect — and come back to the body as a place of safety, strength, and stillness. You don’t need to be flexible, spiritual, or calm to join. Just bring your tired self - we’ll take care of the rest.

What to expect: 
- Movement for all levels
- ⁠Breathwork for the Nervous System
- ⁠Guided mediation
- ⁠and yes a deeper more restful sleep ❤️

Come as you are, leave a little lighter! 

Instructions in English.
